{"tid":1353680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突然諗到琴日話開片嘅陰謀","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T05:24:28.000Z","uid":131782,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"befb7bbc6404c2abc4ae9d5ce79534c0c64cbffc","tid":1353680,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"琴日一路傳話新義安入元朗開片 又話和勝和班人打咗新義安大佬個老婆 跟住屯天元鋪頭5點幾嗰時落晒閘 點解呢？<br />\n<br />\n我淨係諗到一個原因<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係佢哋就喺想搞大件事</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全個屯天元落晒閘</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">水靜河飛咁有咩好？</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">冇錯就係等班鄉黑有時間走</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家試諗下由下午6點開始</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">條街又冇乜人得翻啲車</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁班鄉黑個個揸車走都冇人知啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果班鄉黑真係趁琴日呢個空窗期走咗，咁即係代表<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">元朗好安全</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗好安全</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗好安全</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以所以各位7/27記得入元朗喇，如果驚嘅話，記得記得<span style=\"color: gold;\">帶gear啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n和勝和，14k，新義安 呢度冇人識你啊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">以上觀點，純粹個人感覺，如有其他意見，歡迎提供</span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">屌細力啲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e1c446a93e8cb228c2801efbcdac144a6c2770","tid":1353680,"uid":276943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"唔係得返小小車先覺眼咩"},{"pid":"7ba66df93ea799b76ff216646981734540e03773","tid":1353680,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d0e343dba1bb5daf2dc5d79aae92b160d45eb192","tid":1353680,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80e1c446a93e8cb228c2801efbcdac144a6c2770","tid":1353680,"uid":276943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"唔係得返小小車先覺眼咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:08:33.000Z","msg":"走小路？利申唔熟元朗"},{"pid":"33a4c8b9771d5977ed9d33065f0f7c3a7a9011ba","tid":1353680,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"8cc3e6b32d9fdbbbefd2774b319c5f770e0ca057","tid":1353680,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5283060904b68131dc88ce590f3f30ec6efa8ef6","tid":1353680,"uid":131782